reviewText: funny as hell not real but funny worth the watch
Crazy wild what things he does in the movie steal breaking in rooms how to get over on people

I like "hood" documentaries, but this is not one of those. This is a semi-sarcastic, blatant attempt at being humorous that fails completely. I found it entertaining, but was let down that it was half comedy routine, and a bad one at that. On the other hand, there are some small truths to be garnered from this video, and it can be entertaining as a one time viewing opportunity.
